cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI 

This paper discusses the detection of DDoS attacks on IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of machine learning algorithms for detection suggests that it could also fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of traffic data, which could fall under the category of signal processing (cs.SI).
